sellerCard.oneLiner: Helping People to promote their Businesses
sellerCard.description:
Hi, This is Farooq, an expert Klaviyo Email Marketer & Shopify developer with 5 years of experience. I have been in the E-commerce industry for 5 years and have many satisfying clients on this planet. I know all tactics and techniques to boost sales and conversions. 
My aim is to help people to promote their Online Businesses with my vast experience in Branding. I shall utilize my 100% energy and knowledge to solve any of your problems related to the online market.

Cheers.

description.content:
Greetings and Warm Welcome to the best gig of Shopify!


  • Do you need a branded Shopify Store?
  • Do you have a Shopify Website and need to revamp and customization?
  • Don't you know much about Branding or Shopify Dropshipping? 


The good news is that you are with the right person. I will provide you a complete solution from the setting up of the Shopify Store using Premium theme to adding all essential features and functionalities.


⭐What's included⭐


  • All essential Pages
  • Responsive Design & Customization
  • Creation of collections and sub-collections
  • Basic Logo (in case you don't have)
  • Essential features like Pop-up, Live Chat, Currency Converter, Order Tracking page, trust badges, etc.


I'll design responsive and SEO-optimized shopify website using Premium theme and add all essential features to it.



If you have any special requirements regarding customization, design, features or anything at all, just ping me and we can discuss.


Still have any questions, feel free to inbox me. I will be more than happy to answer any of your questions.


Cheers,

Farooq

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will require Shopify admin access as a staff member to get started.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you use Premium theme by your own?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will use a Premium theme to develop your store and you don't need to pay me for that if you pick the premium package.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What other things do you need to develop shopify store?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
After you add me to your Shopify admin, I will need you to provide me some information about your business, some content like About Us, FAQ, your Shipping policy, etc, and some High-Quality images. 
The more you tell me about your business, the more I can help you in a better way.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What differentiate you than others?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Well, I believe in quality and dedication. I will help you until you get satisfied.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you be available after the completion of project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Of course, I will always be available for your help, no matter during the project or after the project.
Feel free to ask me anything at any time.
